node.text:
@memphisdepay of FC Barcelona during his first press conference at Camp Nou was wearing a @rolex Cosmograph Daytona in 18k rose gold with brown ‘chocolate’ dial. This timepiece was added to the collection in 2019 and it features rose gold hour markers and black sub dials. The Daytona is equipped with calibre 4130, a self-winding mechanical chronograph movement developed and manufactured by Rolex. #Rolex

Retail price: $ 39,350.00
Market price: $ 60,000.00

Photo: @fcbarcelona | @rolex

node.text:
Pep Guardiola of Manchester City is back to work with his million-dollars @richardmille RM 27-01 Tourbillon ‘Rafael Nadal’ in Quartz TPT® and Carbon TPT®. The movement is held in total suspension in the heart of its case, inspired by suspended civil engineering infrastructures. This timepiece has been secretly released back in 2018 and its market price grown up a lot in the last years. #RichardMille

Limited edition: 10 pieces
Retail price: $660,000.00

Photo: @mancity | @richardmille

node.text:
Sylvester Stallone in his latest post wears a @rolex Oyster Perpetual 41mm in stainless steel with green dial, that his huge wrist makes it look smaller. Introduced in 2020 the new Oyster Perpetual has been unveiled with a dynamic and vibrant new look, offering lacquer dials in five new colours: candy pink, turquoise blue, yellow, coral red and Rolex green. #Rolex

Retail price: $5,900.00
Market price: $12,500.00

Photo : @officialslystallone | @rolex

The first @patekphilippe 5711 ‘Green’ auctioned has been sold for $490,000.00 (fees included) today at ‘Important Modern & Vintage Timepieces Monaco’ auction of Antiquorum. This watch retails for $34,893.00 exclusively available for the best clients of Patek Philippe boutiques. Do you think the 5711/1A-014 is really worth that much? #PatekPhilippe

Photo: @patekphilippe

node.text:
@dbook of Phoenix Suns ahead of tonight’s Game Six of the 2021 NBA Finals wears a @patekphilippe Aquanaut Chronograph 5968A in stainless steel with orange strap. This timepiece is the first chronograph of the Aquanaut collection and it has been introduced in 2018. It features the classic Aquanaut’s square pattern in dark grey with orange on both the seconds hand and the sub-counter plus other small details. #PatekPhilippe

Retail price: $53,360.00
Market price: $135,000.00

Photo: @suns | @patekphilippe

node.text:
The Italian footballer Sebastian Giovinco of Saudi Arabian club Al Hilal wears a @geraldcharles_official Maestro GC3.0 in rose gold with green ‘emerald’ dial, part of brand’s Premier 2021. This timepiece is powered by an hand finished ultra-thin automatic chronograph movement called GCA3022/12 made by Vaucher. It features a chronograph without date with three counters for seconds, minutes and hours. #GeraldCharles

Limited edition: 25 pieces
Retail price: $ 43,000.00

Photo: @sebagiovincoofficial | @geraldcharles_official

node.text:
@santandave has recently released the single ‘Clash’ featuring Stormzy, on the set of their music video both UK rappers shown part of their collections, in particular Royal Oak watches of @audemarspiguet. Stormzy holds three AP Royal Oak Double Balance Wheel Openworked in 3 different materials (black ceramic, 18k rose gold and 18k frosted white gold) plus an AP Royal Oak Perpetual Calendar in black ceramic. Dave appears to be holding similar pieces to Stormzy, but his Royal Oak Double Balance Wheel Openworked is made in stainless steel and not frosted 18k white gold and instead of the black ceramic version he has the 37mm rainbow baguette-cut sapphires bezel in 18k white gold. #AudemarsPiguet

node.text:
The football legend @francescototti, World Cup 2006 winner with Italy National Team, wears a @patekphilippe Aquanaut 5168G in 18k white gold. This model is not the first Aquanaut in khaki green. In 2011, Patek released a highly limited “special clients only” Aquanaut Jumbo 5167A in a 40mm stainless steel case with a khaki green dial and strap. Throughout his long career in Rome, Totti used to wear a Rolex Daytona ‘Zenith’ in stainless steel, watch that he lost last year. #PatekPhilippe 

Retail price: $40,615.00
Market price: $95,000.00

Photo: @gettyimages | @patekphilippe
